descr_cg: The control group completed BAIs at the same timepoints; however they did not receive any treatment and were free to quit thestudy at any time to pursue treatment. Any participant who started a new treatment was excluded from the study. Subjects in the control group did not have access or were experiencing a barrier to receiving in-person treatment or were on a wait list.
